Text:
Reality-TV
Gold Coast


The GC follows the lives of a group of talented and attractive young Maori as they work hard and play even harder in Australia's favourite playground, the glittering Gold Coast. 
(http://www.imdb.com/title/tt2366111/)

The Māori (Māori pronunciation: [ˈmaːɔɾi], English: /ˈmaʊəri/)[6] are the native or indigenous Polynesian people of New Zealand.
(http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/M%C4%81ori_people)
